title: Skyrim V 10 Beginners MOD TOOLS
description:
This tools are for beginners who wanted to start modding SKYRIM V (pc version)

It does not contain any other mods like armors, swords, DLC's and such.


File contains very useful free tools to begin modding your Skyrim V pc game.


I do not own any of this tools nor created them, I only gather them from 1 website to another and put them all together in one place ;-)
==================================================================================


TOOLS in folders are
==================================================================================

1. Xbox360 64bit. (FOR XBOX CONTROLLERS)

2. BetterDS3_1.5.3 (FOR PS3 CONTROLLERS)

3. Motioninjoy-0-7-1001 (BLUETOOTH or WIRE BOTH CONTROLLERS)

4. LOOT.v0.8.1.7 

5. Wrye Bash 304.3

6. TES5Edit_091115

7. Nexus Mod Manager 06016 (NONE CRACK VERSION)

8. Mod-Organizer v1.3.10.7

9. SkyUI 5.1-3863-5-1

10. SKSE 1.07.03

==================================================================================

PLEASE SEED SO YOU AND OTHER USERS HAVE A QUICKER AND MORE FASTER DOWNLOAD SPEED

ENJOY AND HAPPY MODDING :-)


FURY
